#: ../../models/architecture.rst:2 c5add38ee8144ae5a87a396425bde777
msgid "Architecture"
msgstr "架构"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:4 c767c4671c51445da8656c7a80627c09
msgid ""
"VoxCPM adopts a **tokenizer-free, diffusion autoregressive** architecture "
"that models speech in continuous latent space rather than discrete tokens. "
"This page first explains the high-level design shared across the VoxCPM "
"family, then summarizes the main architectural improvements introduced in "
"VoxCPM 2."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 采用**无分词器、扩散自回归** 架构，在连续潜空间而非离散 token 上建模语音。本页先说明 VoxCPM 系列共通的高层设计，再概括"
" VoxCPM 2 引入的主要架构改进。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:6 7e34a36b2e3043fcb3c58151303b232c
msgid "VoxCPM Model Architecture"
msgstr "VoxCPM 模型架构"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:11 9c9c8745970840329eab23329fa642c1
msgid "High-level VoxCPM pipeline shared across the model family."
msgstr "VoxCPM 系列共用的高层流水线。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:16 6357d7bebf5c45ca8e5a1d6c1ce5813d
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:18 81805bdfeda54ffa9c0fe5948a506990
msgid ""
"Unlike mainstream TTS approaches that convert speech into discrete tokens, "
"VoxCPM uses an end-to-end architecture that **directly generates continuous "
"speech representations** from text. Built on a `MiniCPM-4 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM>`_ backbone, the system uses "
"hierarchical language modeling and FSQ-constrained continuous latents to "
"separate high-level semantic planning from low-level acoustic rendering."
msgstr ""
"与将语音转为离散 token 的主流 TTS 不同，VoxCPM 采用端到端架构，从文本**直接生成连续语音表示**。系统以 `MiniCPM-4 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM>`_ 为骨干，结合分层语言建模与 FSQ "
"约束的连续潜变量，将高层语义规划与低层声学渲染分离开来。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:20 ff87c232d6f3437886a16f0a36e1d650
msgid ""
"Across VoxCPM 1.0, 1.5, and 2, the family shares the same high-level "
"generation path:"
msgstr "在 VoxCPM 1.0、1.5 与 2 上，系列共用同一条高层生成路径："

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:22 fce4fc91512d4c20b6e90f5829b5e9c9
msgid ""
"**text -> four-stage generative pipeline -> AudioVAE decoder -> waveform**"
msgstr "**文本 → 四阶段生成流水线 → AudioVAE 解码器 → 波形**"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:24 4a618e08da914222b7eeb23c75aee4bd
msgid "The generative backbone consists of four stages:"
msgstr "生成骨干由四个阶段组成："

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:30 61b25d8048c042b48456f9fc6e0c66b0
msgid "#"
msgstr "#"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:31 de42f3b1640c4c6aa1c47001dde1b465
msgid "Stage"
msgstr "阶段"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:32 96cd635e596e41b98af805c2f88cef25
msgid "Description"
msgstr "说明"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:33 d2f9b89ee6d049e9ad097a716875dfc7
msgid "1"
msgstr "1"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:34 cb8bfb2de19848a581e28e79b481d7d8
msgid "**Local Encoder**"
msgstr "**Local Encoder**"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:35 b911251597c843578e020ea9e07a373b
msgid ""
"Encodes input audio patches into compact local representations. Groups "
"consecutive audio frames into patches to reduce the effective sequence "
"length for the language model."
msgstr "将输入音频 patch 编码为紧凑的局部表示；把连续音频帧组成 patch，以降低语言模型的有效序列长度。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:36 54c56636b13c4e0ba6e8dfdd497d055b
msgid "2"
msgstr "2"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:37 f6068b1f3be94217bbbf3696e1d8facc
msgid "**Text-Semantic LM**"
msgstr "**Text-Semantic LM**"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:38 1bf1651925c74790b429b580e7c98ebb
msgid ""
"A causal language model (based on `MiniCPM-4 "
"<https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM>`_) that jointly processes text tokens "
"and audio embeddings to capture high-level semantic intent. This stage "
"handles the \"what to say\" — planning prosody, pacing, and emphasis from "
"the text content."
msgstr ""
"基于 `MiniCPM-4 <https://github.com/OpenBMB/MiniCPM>`_ 的因果语言模型，联合处理文本 token "
"与音频嵌入以捕捉高层语义意图。该阶段负责「说什么」——依据文本内容规划韵律、节奏与重音。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:39 94d231f8a5704709bbbd041998c96052
msgid "3"
msgstr "3"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:40 b58746bf19b242358cd110f32a88907f
msgid "**Residual Acoustic LM**"
msgstr "**Residual Acoustic LM**"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:41 6aef66798ab2498096ceab57c1603680
msgid ""
"Fuses semantic-level and acoustic-level information to model fine-grained "
"acoustic details. Bridges the gap between the text-semantic planning and the"
" final audio generation."
msgstr "融合语义层与声学层信息，建模细粒度声学细节；在文本语义规划与最终音频生成之间起到衔接作用。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:42 cf77dfea06f04ca2858c4f6bbf861765
msgid "4"
msgstr "4"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:43 81e953820bfc48539e3f68fea41fedfa
msgid "**Local DiT (CFM)**"
msgstr "**Local DiT (CFM)**"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:44 426f1a814c974edeaa4a28e31ad422a6
msgid ""
"A Conditional Flow Matching (CFM) diffusion transformer that generates "
"continuous audio latents conditioned on the LM outputs. Produces high-"
"fidelity speech patches at each autoregressive step."
msgstr "以 LM 输出为条件的条件流匹配（CFM）扩散 Transformer，生成连续音频潜变量；在每个自回归步输出高保真语音 patch。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:46 f734011669664accbe4362ba37db64b3
msgid ""
"The generated latents are then decoded by **AudioVAE** into raw waveforms. "
"AudioVAE is a supporting codec component used around the generative "
"backbone: it provides latent representations during training and converts "
"predicted latents back to waveform samples during inference."
msgstr ""
"生成的潜变量再由 **AudioVAE** 解码为原始波形。AudioVAE "
"是围绕生成骨干的配套编解码组件：训练时提供潜表示，推理时将预测的潜变量还原为波形采样。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:48 2fded958803b422f92e311034dab0921
msgid ""
"Across versions, the codec layer evolves from a symmetric audio VAE in "
"VoxCPM 1.x to **AudioVAE V2** in VoxCPM 2, which uses asymmetric 16kHz "
"encode -> 48kHz decode and sample-rate conditioning."
msgstr ""
"跨版本演进中，编解码层从 VoxCPM 1.x 的对称 audio VAE，发展为 VoxCPM 2 的 **AudioVAE V2**：采用非对称 "
"16kHz 编码 → 48kHz 解码，并带采样率条件。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:50 c44b6730ac274f71963f1a599b121640
msgid "Three design choices define the shared VoxCPM architecture:"
msgstr "三项设计选择共同定义了 VoxCPM 的共用架构："

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:52 dec10880c4b04a10bde164dfb53dd1aa
msgid ""
"**Tokenizer-free continuous modeling** preserves fine-grained acoustic "
"detail instead of compressing speech into discrete tokens."
msgstr "**无分词器的连续建模** 保留细粒度声学细节，而非把语音压缩为离散 token。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:53 00ebc9f89ec8474699b4318fa448e1c2
msgid ""
"**Hierarchical semantic-acoustic separation** lets the model split high-"
"level planning from low-level rendering."
msgstr "**分层语义–声学分离** 使模型将高层规划与低层渲染分开处理。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:54 82ecb08a047f4ffd8f332878276fce0c
msgid ""
"**Patch-level autoregressive generation** reduces sequence length and helps "
"the system scale to longer and faster synthesis settings."
msgstr "**Patch 级自回归生成** 缩短序列长度，有助于系统在更长、更快的合成设定下扩展。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:56 b941426724ef4075ae895dc8d6ca819d
msgid ""
"For version-by-version model selection and migration guidance, see "
":doc:`./version_history`."
msgstr "若需按版本选择模型与迁移指引，请参阅 :doc:`./version_history`。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:61 9fcb14fb698f4dd4b524cf618500c6ff
msgid "VoxCPM 2 Improvements"
msgstr "VoxCPM 2 的改进"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:63 884c84d013344254bfb802f6809065c4
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 2 keeps the same overall four-stage structure, but redesigns several "
"internal information pathways. These changes are important because they "
"explain why VoxCPM 2 improves expressiveness, controllability, and output "
"quality without changing the high-level mental model of the system."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 2 保持四阶段整体结构不变，但重新设计了若干内部信息流路径。这些改动很重要：它们说明了为何在不改变系统高层心智模型的前提下，VoxCPM "
"2 能提升表现力、可控性与输出质量。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:69 8be138708b25466e83211afff67bef1f
msgid "Area"
msgstr "方面"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:70 5dbe75e31a4a4837967db320420e419a
msgid "VoxCPM 1.x"
msgstr "VoxCPM 1.x"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:71 f598ee8e98e94306b0647214447bbca1
msgid "VoxCPM 2"
msgstr "VoxCPM 2"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:72 1ee41b65cac04aaa86a92c8822193b14
msgid "**Residual Acoustic LM fusion**"
msgstr "**Residual Acoustic LM 融合**"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:73 a04219dfce9649209c1a3fd3960e466d
msgid "Additive fusion"
msgstr "加法融合"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:74 b5624534b67846ee85c7a61f38b5be66
msgid "Concat + projection fusion for richer semantic-acoustic mixing"
msgstr "拼接 + 投影融合，实现更丰富的语义–声学混合"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:75 cd1699855a464ef89628437d4d85e9af
msgid "**Local DiT conditioning**"
msgstr "**Local DiT 条件化**"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:76 9f858d873e9c4e64a0eba23e42e2af56
msgid "Single fused conditioning token"
msgstr "单一融合条件 token"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:77 996b4f4b784943c9925c90975b7fa7e3
msgid "Multi-token conditioning prefix to preserve more information"
msgstr "多 token 条件前缀，保留更多信息"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:78 33a6b17523d740a593210d5fcdc98d8d
msgid "**Reference audio pathway**"
msgstr "**参考音频通路**"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:79 2c2a6e7d88ac4992b260b4a9d2bccfff
msgid "Prompt continuation only"
msgstr "仅 prompt 续写"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:80 fee81d929500483daa60af2ceaaa4373
msgid "Structurally isolated reference-audio channel"
msgstr "结构隔离的参考音频通道"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:81 5e2c7d360e4d4bae9ed887e9280875bd
msgid "**AudioVAE**"
msgstr "**AudioVAE**"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:82 002488bbc0a34c798a3975efb2e4a2e0
msgid "Symmetric encode/decode"
msgstr "对称编解码"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:83 3d1b443697a24b57a953947e043e9da5
msgid "AudioVAE V2 with asymmetric 16kHz encode -> 48kHz decode"
msgstr "AudioVAE V2：非对称 16kHz 编码 → 48kHz 解码"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:86 996628e6848a491bbb07a6a45749dd4b
msgid "Residual Acoustic LM Fusion"
msgstr "Residual Acoustic LM 融合"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:88 28e6951cc82b4f118789999395aafe19
msgid ""
"In VoxCPM 1.x, the Residual Acoustic LM combines the semantic LM output and "
"local acoustic features through **addition**. VoxCPM 2 replaces this with "
"**concatenation followed by a learnable projection**."
msgstr ""
"在 VoxCPM 1.x 中，Residual Acoustic LM 通过**相加** 合并语义 LM 输出与局部声学特征。VoxCPM 2 "
"则改为** 拼接后再经可学习投影**。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:90 b36666136c554671b2607a85abdffe02
msgid ""
"This gives the model more freedom to decide how semantic intent and acoustic"
" evidence should interact, instead of forcing them into the same "
"representation through element-wise addition. In practice, this supports "
"richer acoustic detail and stronger expressiveness."
msgstr "这使模型能更自由地决定语义意图与声学证据如何交互，而不必通过逐元素加法强行压入同一表示。在实践中，这有助于更丰富的声学细节与更强的表现力。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:93 c88d33e7c6ab4ac0a5509c750d596a87
msgid "Local DiT Conditioning"
msgstr "Local DiT 条件化"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:95 57c9d6c96fcf408d96a46e934741b302
msgid ""
"The Local DiT is a diffusion transformer operating within each audio patch. "
"Instead of using a single early-fused conditioning signal, VoxCPM 2 feeds "
"the DiT a **multi-token conditioning prefix** derived from the semantic and "
"acoustic pathways."
msgstr ""
"Local DiT 是在每个音频 patch 内工作的扩散 Transformer。VoxCPM 2 不再使用单一早期融合条件信号，而是向 DiT "
"提供来自语义与声学路径的**多 token 条件前缀**。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:97 b7d80e2ee16c411cb0b434dbc3eea5f3
msgid ""
"This preserves more information for attention to work with inside the DiT, "
"reducing information collapse from premature fusion. The result is a more "
"expressive and controllable final acoustic generation stage."
msgstr "这样在 DiT 内部为注意力保留更多信息，减轻过早融合导致的信息坍缩；最终声学生成阶段也因此更具表现力与可控性。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:100 c8c257a6b8bc45d8a6826507f389ec4e
msgid "Isolated Reference Audio Channel"
msgstr "隔离的参考音频通道"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:102 6acc9c6870fe462a8da7b1c1dc3a01f3
msgid ""
"VoxCPM 1.x primarily supports voice cloning through prompt continuation. "
"VoxCPM 2 adds a **structurally isolated reference-audio pathway**, "
"separating timbre reference from continuation context."
msgstr ""
"VoxCPM 1.x 主要通过 prompt 续写支持声音克隆。VoxCPM 2 增加**结构隔离的参考音频通路**，将音色参考与续写上下文分开。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:104 8d8f974711d14116b96dce12c6c680fe
msgid ""
"This architectural change is what enables stronger reference-only cloning "
"behavior and makes it easier to combine voice identity control with other "
"generation modes."
msgstr "这一架构变化使「仅参考」克隆行为更强，也更容易将声线身份控制与其他生成模式结合。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:107 b71f48750da043a19b9b5ba917680e30
msgid "Why AudioVAE V2 Matters"
msgstr "为何 AudioVAE V2 重要"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:109 0300a6125dc549a9b7428b81b2e1e347
msgid ""
"AudioVAE V2 is not just a higher-sample-rate decoder. Its asymmetric "
"encode/decode design keeps the language-model-side sequence efficient while "
"still producing 48kHz output directly."
msgstr "AudioVAE V2 不只是更高采样率的解码器。其非对称编解码设计在保持语言模型侧序列高效的同时，仍能直接输出 48kHz。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:111 184b46a89c5b434581e778c99958b3ce
msgid ""
"This is a key architectural improvement because it raises output fidelity "
"without requiring a proportional increase in sequence length or a separate "
"upsampling stage."
msgstr "这是关键的架构改进：在不必同比拉长序列长度、也不必单独上采样级的前提下提升输出保真度。"

#: ../../models/architecture.rst:116 a86fd526e4b648f89b03ad7f03d13c90
msgid "Where to Go Next"
msgstr "延伸阅读"

